---
import CssNakedDay from '../components/CssNakedDay/CssNakedDay.astro';
import DecoratedLine from '../components/DecoratedLine/DecoratedLine.astro';
import HtmlHead from '../components/HtmlHead/HtmlHead.astro';
import Logo from '../components/Logo/Logo.astro';
import OldStyleButtons from '../components/OldStyleButtons/OldStyleButtons.astro';
import SiteNav from '../components/SiteNav/SiteNav.astro';
import SvgDefs from '../components/SvgDefs/SvgDefs.astro';
import Webrings from '../components/Webrings/Webrings.astro';
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en-US" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/WebPage">
	<HtmlHead
		title="Colophon | Marco Campos"
		description="Colophon"
	/>
	<body>
		<a href="/yapping" rel="nofollow" hidden>Don't follow this link</a>

		<SiteNav />
		<CssNakedDay />

		<header>
			<Logo
				subtitle="Colophon"
				shortSubtitle="Colo."
				title="Home Page"
			/>
			<h1 data-pagefind-meta="title">Colophon</h1>
		</header>

		<main data-pagefind-body>
			<h2>WTF Is a "colophon"?</h2>

			<p>The term comes from publishing, it's basically a page on a book telling what tools were used to make the book.</p>

			<h2>How is the site made?</h2>

			<p>The tools used are:</p>
			<ul>
				<li><a href="https://astro.build/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Astro</a> as the build tool.</li>
				<li><a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Visual Studio Code</a> as the editor.</li>
				<li>The code for the website is available on <a href="https://github.com/madcampos/madcampos/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a></li>
				<li>The site is hosted on <a href="https://cloudflare.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cloudflare</a></li>
			</ul>

			<p>There is more about the styles in the <a href="/styleguide/">styleguide</a> and <a href="/brand/">brand</a> pages.</p>

			<h2>Principles</h2>

			<p>The main principle for the website is to have a space to express my ideas and try out things.</p>
			<p>The blog is there as sort of a "note keeping" space, where I write to remember and have a better understanding on the things I learn.</p>
		</main>

		<footer>
			<DecoratedLine />

			<OldStyleButtons />
			<Webrings />
			<hit-counter></hit-counter>
		</footer>
		<SvgDefs />
		<iab-escape></iab-escape>
	</body>
</html>
